snippet.title: César Soto Valero
snippet.description: I specialize in simplifying complexity. I break down challenging software engineering and AI concepts into clear, practical insights that you can apply right away. My mission is to empower you with strong fundamentals and share the real-world lessons I’ve gained from over two decades of higher education, academic research, and hands-on industry experience.
